At the weekend, a cellphone shop at City View was robbed. 
Marshall Security spokesperson, Kyle van Reenen, said a number of armed suspects stormed the shop at about 8am on Sunday. 
"The staff were tied up. Cellphones were taken. No one was injured," he said. 

He said in a separate incident at the Windermere Shopping Centre, a woman was robbed of her gold chain. 
Van Reenen said the assailant had a firearm and fired two shots into the air. No injuries were reported. 
The Mercury